<td><b>Louis Pasteur (1822-1895)</b>
  <p>chemist
<p><b><font color="#4618C6">1847</font></b>:&nbsp; studied <b>crystals</b>
<p><b><font color="#4618C6">1864</font></b>:&nbsp; studied <b>fermentation</b>
<ul>
<li>
thought to be chemical process</li>

<li>
yeast is a catalyst</li>

<li>
determined yeast was living organism</li>

<li>
fermentation is metabolic process</li>
</ul></td>

