<ul>
<li>
growth of microbes can be controlled:&nbsp; <b>pasteurization</b></li>

<li>
<b>living things come from living things</b></li>
</ul>
<b><font color="#4618C6">1882</font></b>:&nbsp; work on <b>rabies</b>
<ul>
